<item>
            <title>[LU-7790] Interop 2.8.0&lt;-&gt;2.7.1 : recovery-small test_130a:stat should fail</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7790</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/70cd574e-d2f8-11e5-bf08-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/70cd574e-d2f8-11e5-bf08-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_130a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;stat should fail
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== recovery-small test 130a: enqueue resend on not existing file ===================================== 06:14:51 (1455372891)
CMD: onyx-40vm1.onyx.hpdd.intel.com,onyx-40vm2 sync
CMD: onyx-40vm7 lctl set_param fail_val=0 fail_loc=0x80000160
fail_val=0
fail_loc=0x80000160
  File: &apos;/mnt/lustre/d130a.recovery-small&apos;
  Size: 4096      	Blocks: 8          IO Block: 4096   directory
Device: 2c54f966h/743766374d	Inode: 144115993919094790  Links: 2
Access: (0755/drwxr-xr-x)  Uid: (    0/    root)   Gid: (    0/    root)
Access: 2016-02-13 06:14:52.000000000 -0800
Modify: 2016-02-13 06:14:52.000000000 -0800
Change: 2016-02-13 06:14:52.000000000 -0800
 Birth: -
CMD: onyx-40vm7 lctl set_param fail_val=0 fail_loc=0x80000157
fail_val=0
fail_loc=0x80000157
 recovery-small test_130a: @@@@@@ FAIL: stat should fail 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also, according to a comment on &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7710&quot; title=&quot;recovery-small test_130a: stat should fail&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7710&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7710&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, this new ticket has been created to track this failure which appears to be occurring due to the interop test script not ensuring that the fix is present on both versions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Server: 2.7.1 , b2_7_fe/34&lt;br/&gt;
Client: 2.8.0, b2_8,  build#2 , RHEL 7</environment>
